'''{{lang|en|Plarium}}'''是一家[[以色列|以色列]]手機、社交和網路遊戲開發及發行公司，成立於2009年，總部設在[[海爾茲利亞|海爾茲利亞]]；在俄羅斯、烏克蘭、英國和美國皆設有分部<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.gamesindustry.biz/articles/2016-01-16-plarium-expands-to-london/|title=Plarium expands to London|publisher=gamesindustry.biz|date=2016-01-16|access-date=2021-04-10|archive-date=2018-09-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180901080402/https://www.gamesindustry.biz/articles/2016-01-16-plarium-expands-to-london/}}</ref>。該公司以[[大型多人線上遊戲|大型多人線上遊戲]]聞名，知名作品如《[[突襲：暗影傳說|突襲：暗影傳說]]》、《{{le|維京雄起：家族之戰|Vikings: War of Clans}}》、《{{le|魔鬼終結者創世契機：未來之戰|Terminator Genisys: Future War}}》、《{{le|士兵公司|Soldiers Inc.}}》<ref>[http://www.timesofisrael.com/where-alien-vs-predator-meets-israels-gaming-industry/ Where Alien vs. Predator meets Israel’s gaming industry] {{Wayback|url=http://www.timesofisrael.com/where-alien-vs-predator-meets-israels-gaming-industry/ |date=20181010062049 }}, Times of Israel</ref>、《{{le|斯巴達：帝國戰爭|Sparta: War of Empires}}》<ref>[http://www.gamasutra.com/blogs/OrenTodoros/20140822/224001/Animation_Sound_and_Scoring_How_Plarium_Brought_Sparta_to_Life.php Animation, Sound and Scoring: How Plarium Brought Sparta to Life] {{Wayback|url=http://www.gamasutra.com/blogs/OrenTodoros/20140822/224001/Animation_Sound_and_Scoring_How_Plarium_Brought_Sparta_to_Life.php |date=20160827141410 }}, Gamasutra</ref>和《{{le|風暴瀑布：戰爭時代|Stormfall: Age of War}}》<ref>[https://venturebeat.com/2015/01/12/plarium-launches-new-version-of-smash-hit-stormfall-on-mobile/ Plarium launches new version of smash-hit Stormfall on mobile] {{Wayback|url=https://venturebeat.com/2015/01/12/plarium-launches-new-version-of-smash-hit-stormfall-on-mobile/ |date=20210410092229 }}, Venture Beat</ref>。社交遊戲可在[[Facebook|Facebook]]、[[Vkontakte|Vkontakte]]、[[Odnoklassniki|Odnoklassniki]]和{{le|Mail.ru集團|Mail.ru Group|Mail.Ru}}上使用，而其手機遊戲可在[[iOS|iOS]]和[[Android|Android]]平台上使用。

2012年11月，{{lang|en|Plarium}}的《風暴瀑布：戰爭時代》上線後成為Facebook上增長最快的社交遊戲<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.haaretz.com/misc/iphone-article/tech-roundup-plarium-gaming-company-scores-a-top-20-facebook-hit.premium-1.509707|title=Tech roundup / Plarium gaming company scores a Top 20 Facebook hit|publisher=Haaretz.com|date=2013-03-15|access-date=2021-04-10|archive-date=2016-07-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160723211838/http://www.haaretz.com/misc/iphone-article/tech-roundup-plarium-gaming-company-scores-a-top-20-facebook-hit.premium-1.509707}}</ref>。2013年，Facebook將《士兵公司》排入年度最佳社交遊戲行列<ref>{{cite web|url=https://developers.facebook.com/blog/post/2013/12/09/facebook-games-of-the-year-2013/|title=Facebook Games of the Year 2013|publisher=Facebook.com|date=2013-12-09|access-date=2021-04-10|archive-date=2021-04-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210410092203/https://developers.facebook.com/blog/post/2013/12/09/facebook-games-of-the-year-2013/}}</ref>。

{{le|貴族娛樂|Aristocrat Leisure}}於2017年8月10日被以5億美元的預付款以及向股東的收益分配安排收購{{lang|en|Plarium}}。

